OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1776694271
OL,3,COfficers discover illegal tobacco
OL,4,Cproducts under trap door in shop
OL,6,FIllegal tobacco products have been
OL,7,Fseized after being found under a trap
OL,8,Fdoor in a Kent shop.
OL,10,FThe stash was discovered at a business
OL,11,Fon London Road in Dover as part of
OL,12,Fefforts to target the sale and supply
OL,13,Fof illicit cigarettes, tobacco and
OL,14,Fvapes.
OL,16,FThe business owners denied selling any
OL,17,Fillegal products and are now subject
OL,18,Fto an investigation by Trading
OL,19,FStandards.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
