PN,41902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1776694271
OL,3,COfficers discover illegal tobacco
OL,4,Cproducts under trap door in shop
OL,6,FThe operation, run by Dover's
OL,7,FCommunity Safety Unit and Kent County
OL,8,FCouncil's Trading Standards, involved
OL,9,Fa series of co-ordinated visits to
OL,10,Fbusinesses across the area on Friday
OL,11,F10 April 2026 and thousands of pounds
OL,12,Fworth of products were discovered.
OL,14,FSeven premises were inspected as part
OL,15,Fof the operation.
OL,17,FOfficers discovered several similar
OL,18,Fhides located across the businesses
OL,19,Fthat were visited, with hundreds of
OL,20,Fillegal products being seized and
OL,21,Feventually destroyed.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
