OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1776694271
OL,3,COfficers discover illegal tobacco
OL,4,Cproducts under trap door in shop
OL,6,FChief Inspector Liz Cokayne-Delves
OL,7,Fsaid: "The measures taken to conceal
OL,8,Fillegal products make it clear that
OL,9,Fthose responsible are fully aware of
OL,10,Fthe harm they cause.
OL,12,F"These goods are unregulated and often
OL,13,Fdangerous to consume.
OL,15,F"Kent Police will continue to work
OL,16,Fwith partners such as Trading
OL,17,FStandards to identify and disrupt
OL,18,Fbusinesses supplying illicit products.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
