PN,41904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1776694271
OL,3,COfficers discover illegal tobacco
OL,4,Cproducts under trap door in shop
OL,6,FJim Whiddett, Operations Manager for
OL,7,FKent Trading Standards, said: "From
OL,8,Ffalse walls to fake shower units, it
OL,9,Fnever ceases to surprise me where
OL,10,Fofficers find hides.
OL,12,F"But wherever it's stashed, the
OL,13,Fdevastating impacts of illegal tobacco
OL,14,Fis the same: it undercuts legitimate
OL,15,Fbusinesses, puts cash into criminals'
OL,16,Fpockets and makes harmful products
OL,17,Feasier for young people, and anyone
OL,18,Ftrying to quit, to buy.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
